t is said that several Snorunt gather under giant leaves and live together in harmony."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It is said that several Snorunt gather under giant leaves and live together in harmony."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It is said that several Snorunt gather under giant leaves and live together in harmony."},{"version":"x","text":"It is said that several Snorunt gather under giant leaves and live together in harmony."},{"version":"y","text":"In the snow country, certain folklore says a house will prosper if a Snorunt lives there."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Snorunt live in regions with heavy snowfall. In seasons without snow, such as spring and summer, this Pok\u00e9mon steals away to live quietly among stalactites and stalagmites deep in caverns."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Snorunt survives by eating only snow and ice. Old folklore claims that a house visited by this Pok\u00e9mon is sure to prosper for many generations to come."},{"version":"sun","text":"Their numbers seem to have rapidly increased in Alola. Custom has it that houses where Snorunt live will be prosperous for generations to come."},{"version":"moon","text":"It can only survive in cold areas. It bounces happily around, even in environments as cold as -150 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It feeds mainly on ice and snow. It\u2019s only able to survive in a limited number of places in the warm Alola region."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Rich people from cold areas all share childhood memories of playing with Snorunt."},{"version":"sword","text":"It\u2019s said that if they are seen at midnight, they\u2019ll cause heavy snow. They eat snow and ice to survive."},{"version":"shield","text":"It can only survive in cold areas. It bounces happily around, even in environments as cold as \u2212150 degrees Fahrenheit."},{"version":"legends-arceus","text":"Arrives alongside the first snow. It's thought that homes Snorunt visit will prosper for many generations. By tradition, one might offer a lump of ice made from pure water at one's front door."}],"evo":{"name":"snorunt","level":0,"min_level":null,"trigger":null,"item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":null,"turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[{"name":"glalie","level":1,"min_level":42,"trigger":"level-up","item":null,"held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]},{"name":"froslass","level":1,"min_level":null,"trigger":"use-item","item":"dawn-stone","held_item":null,"known_move":null,"known_move_type":null,"location":null,"min_affection":null,"min_beauty":null,"min_happiness":null,"needs_overworld_rain":false,"time_of_day":"","turn_upside_down":false,"evolves_to":[]}]},"sprite":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/361.png","shiny":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/PokeAPI/sprites/master/sprites/pokemon/shiny/361.png","capture":190,"happiness":70,"growth":"medium","gender":4,"hatch":20,"ev":{"hp":1},"forms":[]}